zulucrypt (5.0.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release.
  * debian/control:
      - Updated the long description of libzulucrypt-plugins package
        to add generic_header plugin.
      - Updated the long description of zulumount-gui package to add
        support to unlock cryfs, encfs, gocryptfs and ecryptfs.
      - Inserted the field Suggests in zulumount-gui package.
      - Updated the long description the all packages.
  * debian/copyright:
      - Updated file.
  * debian/rules:
      - Updated to enable polkit support at build time.
      - Updated file.
  * debian/patches:
      - Updated patch fix_spelling.
  * Created new symbol files for libzulucrypt1.2.0,
    libzuluCrypt-exe.so.1.2.0,libzulucryptpluginmanager1.0.0.
  * Updated the files zulu*-gui-pkexec. Thanks Michael Biebl.
    (Closes: #844698)
  * Updated the file zulucrypt-gui.install to added files en_US.qm
    and fr_FR.qm in zulucrypt-gui package.
  * Updated the file zulumount-gui.install to added files en_US.qm
    and fr_FR.qm in zulumount-gui package.

 -- Marcio de Souza Oliveira <m.desouza20@gmail.com>  Mon, 12 Dec 2016 11:30:59 +0000

